homosexual or bisexual males 42182 or 62 percent 
intravenous drug abusers 12721 or 19 percent 
homosexual male and drug abusers 4980 or 7 percent 
heterosexual cases 2815 or 4 percent 
transfusion or blood cases 1829 or 3 percent 
hemophilia patients 713 or 1 percent 
undetermined transmission cause 2143 or 3 percent 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
childhood cases under age 13 1079 or 2 percent 
cases among whites 39882 or 58 percent 
cases among blacks 17764 or 26 percent 
cases among hispanics 9944 or 15 percent 
cases among other 630 or 1 percent 
 
note these statistics are through july 18 and have been 
rounded by the cdc to the nearest whole percent cumulative totals 
are for aids cases reported since june 1981 and include 75 cases 
subsequently found to have occurred prior to that date the 
other classsification under age and race includes asians 
american indians and native alaskans 
