during the weekend 
iran on monday said it would accept a yearold un resolution 
for a ceasefire in the war which has killed or wounded an 
estimated 1 million people 
the un resolution calls for an immediate truce and troop 
withdrawal and sets out a peace plan to end the war including the 
return of captured soldiers 
