to mass killings of inshore fish from diseases of an unknown source 
generally these incidents can be traced to bottom pollutants 
that cause lesions on the fish the bacteria get in those lesions 
and take control he said 
geracis studies of the dolphins showed lesions on the body and 
in the mouths 
